                "invention-title": [
                    "Modularized combination system of NiV-LDH redox medium, hydrogen production and formaldehyde fuel cell and construction method of modularized combination system",
                    "NiV-LDH氧化还原介质、氢气生产与甲醛燃料电池的模块化结合系统及其构建方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a NiV-LDH redox medium, a modularized combination system of hydrogen production and a formaldehyde fuel cell and a construction method of the modularized combination system. An H2 electrolytic tank for H2 production and a direct formaldehyde liquid fuel cell are combined through a NiV-LDH redox medium electrode. The structure comprises a H2 production step (depending on the cathodic hydrogen evolution reaction and the anodic oxidation of NiV-LDH-&gt; NiOOH) and a subsequent discharge step of the direct formaldehyde liquid fuel cell (depending on the cathodic reduction of NiOOH-&gt; NiV-LDH and the anodic oxygen evolution reaction). The cycle of the two steps provides a hybrid energy storage/conversion system, and renewable energy sources can be converted into H2, HCOOH and stable electric energy, so that the energy efficiency and the economic added value of the whole modular system are greatly improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种NiV‑LDH氧化还原介质、氢气生产与甲醛燃料电池的模块化结合系统及其构建方法，通过NiV‑LDH氧化还原介质电极将用于H2生产的H2电解池和直接甲醛液体燃料电池结合起来。该结构包括H2生产步骤(取决于阴极析氢反应以及NiV‑LDH→NiOOH的阳极氧化)和直接甲醛液体燃料电池的后续放电步骤(取决于NiOOH→NiV‑LDH的阴极还原以及阳极析氧反应)。这两个步骤的循环提供了一个混合能量存储/转换系统，可以将可再生能源转换为H2、HCOOH以及稳定的电能，从而大大提升整个模块化系统的能量效率和经济附加值。"
                }
            ]
